# 📄 Smart IT Helpdesk — Full Project Documentation

---

## 1. Project Overview

**Application Name** : Smart IT Helpdesk
**Platform**         : ServiceNow
**Built Using**      : App Engine Studio
**Type**             : Custom Scoped Application
**Scope**            : x_1962921_smart_0

This application was built to streamline IT support operations within an organization.
Employees can raise IT issues as incidents or request new IT items as service requests.
The system automatically manages, assigns, tracks, and resolves these tickets with
minimal manual work from IT agents.

---

## 2. Problem Statement

In most organizations, IT support is managed manually:
- Employees email IT teams for issues
- No ticket tracking system
- No priority management
- No SLA enforcement
- No automated assignment

This project solves all of these problems by building a complete automated
IT helpdesk on ServiceNow.

