## 4. Tables Created

### 4.1 Incident Table

**Purpose** : For employees to raise IT issues (broken things)
**Extended From** : Task table (inherited Number, Priority, State, Assigned To)
**Auto Number Prefix** : SINC

| Field       | Type                  | Description                        |
|-------------|-----------------------|------------------------------------|
| Caller      | Reference → sys_user  | Employee who raised the ticket     |
| Category    | Choice                | Hardware / Software / Network      |
| Priority    | Choice                | 1-Critical / 2-High / 3-Moderate / 4-Low |
| State       | Choice                | New / In Progress / Resolved / Closed |
| Assigned To | Reference → sys_user  | IT Agent handling the ticket       |
| Description | String                | Detailed description of the issue  |

**Category Choice Values:**

| Value    | Label    |
|----------|----------|
| hardware | Hardware |
| software | Software |
| network  | Network  |

**Priority Choice Values:**

| Value | Label       |
|-------|-------------|
| 1     | 1-Critical  |
| 2     | 2-High      |
| 3     | 3-Moderate  |
| 4     | 4-Low       |

**State Choice Values:**

| Value       | Label       |
|-------------|-------------|
| new         | New         |
| in_progress | In Progress |
