## 7. UI Policy

### Policy: Make Description Mandatory for High Priority

| Property  | Value                                  |
|-----------|----------------------------------------|
| Table     | Incident                               |
| Condition | Priority is 2-High OR Priority is 1-Critical |
| Action    | Description field → Mandatory = TRUE   |

**Result:** When agent selects High or Critical priority, the Description
field gets a red asterisk (*) and the form cannot be submitted without
filling in the Description field.

