## 10. Flow Designer — Service Request Approval Flow

**Flow Name** : Service Request Approval Flow
**Trigger**   : Record Created on Service Request table

```
FLOW STEPS:
───────────────────────────────────────────
Step 1 → Ask For Approval
         • Approval Field : Approval Status
         • Approvers      : Manager of Requested For user
         • Rule           : Anyone approves
         • Waits for response before continuing

Step 2 → Send Email Notification
         • To      : Requested For (the employee)
         • Subject : Your Service Request has been created
         • Body    : Request received, pending approval.
                     Our team will review shortly.
───────────────────────────────────────────
```

